snippet.title: Werewolf Party - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Test your deception skills in this thrilling first-person multiplayer game. Invite 4-11 friends to play diverse roles—from a cunning werewolf to an observant villager, each equipped with unique powers. Pay attention to detail, listen for vocal cues, and use your perception to win.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2920510/Werewolf_Party/
